ATTRIBUTION (致謝)

This project, "凡人修仙編年史 (Fanren Cultivation Chronicle)", is a fan-made,
non-commercial derivative work. Its game engine is forked from the open-source
project "react-xiuxian-game (修仙文字游戏)" by JeasonLoop
(https://github.com/JeasonLoop/react-xiuxian-game), released under the MIT
License. The original author's MIT terms are preserved above, with deepest
gratitude.

NOTE ON THE SOURCE NOVEL (原著著作權聲明)

This game is a fan adaptation inspired by the web novel 《凡人修仙傳》 by
忘語 (Wang Yu). The MIT License above covers ONLY this project's source code,
tooling, and the original transformative story-summary data authored for this
game. It does NOT grant any rights to 《凡人修仙傳》 itself; all rights to the
novel remain with 忘語 and the respective rights holders. This repository
contains NO verbatim text of the novel. This is a non-commercial fan work; if
the rights holders object, the corresponding content will be removed on request.
